@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hawbuw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp((tmp + v2))
    v2 = (((tmp + 0.03 - tmp + 0.31) - (v1 + 0.17 - v2 + 0.60)) / 0.73)
    v2 = (v2 / wp.exp(v1))
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.43)) - 0.90)
    data[tid] = v0
